@startuml
title skill-server -> ALB -> gateway 长连接 + gateway Redis 定向 relay

actor User
participant Miniapp
participant "Skill Server S1" as S1
participant "ALB" as ALB
participant "Gateway G2\n(skill owner gateway)" as G2
participant "Redis" as R
participant "Gateway G1\n(agent owner gateway)" as G1
participant "PC Agent" as Agent
participant "Skill Server S2\n(other skill instance)" as S2

== 1. 启动与 owner 注册 ==

S1 -> ALB: 建立 WebSocket /ws/internal/skill
ALB -> G2: 分配到健康 gateway target
G2 -> G2: 注册 local skill link = L1
G2 -> R: SETEX gw:skill:owner:G2 alive ttl
G2 -> R: SADD gw:skill:owners G2
G2 -> R: SUBSCRIBE gw:relay:G2

== 2. 下行：skill -> agent ==

User -> Miniapp: 发送消息
Miniapp -> S1: POST /api/skill/sessions/{id}/messages
S1 -> G2: invoke(agentId=101, sessionId=5001, action=chat)
G2 -> G2: 绑定 5001 -> L1
G2 -> R: SETEX gw:session:skill-owner:5001 G2 ttl
G2 -> R: PUBLISH agent:101
R -> G1: deliver invoke
G1 -> Agent: WS send invoke

== 3. 上行：agent -> skill ==

Agent -> G1: tool_event(sessionId=5001)

alt G1 本地存在 5001 -> local skill link
  G1 -> S1: 通过本地绑定 link 直接发送 GatewayMessage
else G1 本地不存在绑定
  G1 -> R: GET gw:session:skill-owner:5001
  alt sticky owner 有效
    R --> G1: G2
  else sticky owner 无效
    G1 -> R: SMEMBERS gw:skill:owners
    R --> G1: {G2, G3}
    G1 -> G1: 用 Rendezvous Hashing 选择 G2
    G1 -> R: SETEX gw:session:skill-owner:5001 G2 ttl
  end
  G1 -> R: PUBLISH gw:relay:G2 (GatewayMessage)
  R -> G2: deliver relayed GatewayMessage
  alt G2 本地存在 5001 -> L1
    G2 -> S1: 通过 L1 转发 GatewayMessage
  else G2 本地无 5001 绑定
    G2 -> G2: 选择默认 active skill link = L1
    G2 -> G2: 建立 5001 -> L1
    G2 -> S1: 通过 L1 转发 GatewayMessage
  end
end

== 4. skill 集群内广播 ==

S1 -> S1: translate + persist + buffer
S1 -> R: PUBLISH session:5001 (StreamMessage)
R -> S1: deliver session broadcast
R -> S2: deliver session broadcast
S1 -> Miniapp: push StreamMessage
S2 -> Miniapp: 若本实例持有该 session 的前端订阅，也可推送

== 5. owner 失效后的重选 ==

group G2 故障
  G2 -x R: gw:skill:owner:G2 TTL 过期
  Agent -> G1: 下一条 tool_event(sessionId=5001)
  G1 -> R: GET gw:session:skill-owner:5001
  R --> G1: G2
  G1 -> R: EXISTS gw:skill:owner:G2
  R --> G1: false
  G1 -> R: SMEMBERS gw:skill:owners
  R --> G1: {G3}
  G1 -> G1: 重新选主为 G3
  G1 -> R: SETEX gw:session:skill-owner:5001 G3 ttl
  G1 -> R: PUBLISH gw:relay:G3 (GatewayMessage)
end

note over S1,S2
当前 skill-server 存在本地内存态：
SequenceTracker / OpenCodeEventTranslator / MessagePersistenceService
因此同一 session 在 steady-state 下应尽量回到同一 skill 实例。
end note

note over G1,R
Redis relay 仅是 gateway 集群补跳：
- 主通道仍是 skill-server <-> gateway 长连接
- Pub/Sub 语义为 at-most-once
end note

@enduml
